{"tid":492121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[告急]大家緊記，寧投泛民，不投建制，大局為重，關鍵四席！","createTime":"2017-12-07T08:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T17:22:51.000Z","uid":49388,"like":7,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d4c713587646d462295b53de4cc3440c19e39a","tid":492121,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"係建制中共既魔爪下，香港餘下既時間已經不多<br />\n<br />\n再分裂再內鬥已經無意思，內訌只會令狼英偷笑，奶媽暗爽！<br />\n<br />\n為了香港，為了良心，為了民主<br />\n<br />\n我地要團結<br />\n<br />\n唔好理五毛叫你白票<br />\n<br />\n理性地守住關鍵四席，為我為你為下一代！<br />\n<br />\n為香港人，本土泛民集氣投俾泛民！<br />\n<br />\n寧投泛民！ 不投建制！ 大局為重！關鍵四席<br />\n<br />\n#觀看廿三條<br />\n#視察一地兩檢<br />\n#理性地審査國歌法<br />\n#制衡激進的拉布<br />\n#泛民一定做得到！"},{"pid":"b4e9e9af9c2a8dd3acaa8ea1ff98dc5622455c9e","tid":492121,"uid":102096,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f8234f324dfeac91bab0bd310d3ac9645b4fefc","tid":492121,"uid":50719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:26:43.000Z","msg":"關鍵一席變關鍵四席，咁有邊一席係唔關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一變四，四變十二，來到這禮拜更加諷刺"},{"pid":"d833e04ca130bdf28e5c6a9d8154c5bc91407459","tid":492121,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/162927_aa3bf44436937500de0e81634963cf1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F162927_aa3bf44436937500de0e81634963cf1b.jpg&h=6a328788&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/162928_f921711a6af53790230253e3cb2c52b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F162928_f921711a6af53790230253e3cb2c52b7.jpg&h=745a146e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13ada0c52c3a6f721726c3d464702b9bfa31a0b5","tid":492121,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor